55. Khalili M, Saunders JA, Liwo A, Oldziej S, Scheraga HA: A united  residue force-Ô¨Åeld for calcium-protein interactions. Protein Sci
2004, 13:2725-2735. The last of a series of papers describing the development and optimization of the UNRES (united-residue) model, which was derived by

